            <h1 class="rd-page-title">Merchants’ Court Lament</h1>
            <div class="rd-ledger">TEMPLE LEDGER: COMMERCE CONDEMNED</div>
            <p class="rd-page-sub">Gold weeps when idols burn.</p>
            <div class="rd-docket-rule"></div>
